          "Logan Boese"
        ],
        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "You've always been more comfortable with a camera between you and everything else, especially People. In your experience, people are much more enjoyable when they've been frozen and can't talk to you. Your photography, consequently, has always been your haven. You've never been more comfortable than when you were taking photographs. Consequently, you're really good at it. You wield composition and lighting as easily as others wield a pen or a brush. You poured your heart and soul into every photo you ever took. And it caught attention within the world of art and photography. Maybe, in life, you had designs of being an artist, professio Kindred who decided that your particular way of seeing the world needed to be preserved for all time. Because your gift is rare, and especially valuable to a clan with such unique vision. Your talent lay in showing everyone EXACTLY what you see and how you see it. Unfortunately, ever since the Embrace, you've found your talents lacking from what it once was, and your vision has shifted. You're still able to take very good pictures, (You even make a decent \"living,\" selling them under a false identity,) But they're nothing compared to your pre embrace work.  You've adapted with the times, camera wise. You can work anything with a lens, but you've definitely got your favourites."
        ],
